'''約翰·沙希迪'''（{{lang-en|'''John Shahidi'''}}）是一名美国企业家和软件工程师。他是 [[Shots_Studios|Shots Studios]] 的联合创始人和[[首席执行官|首席执行官]]。<ref name="techcrunch">{{cite web|title=Justin Bieber-Backed “Shots Of Me” Launches Selfie Sharing App|url=http://techcrunch.com/2013/11/12/justin-bieber-shots-of-me/|accessdate=26 August 2014|author=Constine, John|date=12 November 2013|publisher=TechCrunch|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200814214607/https://techcrunch.com/2013/11/12/justin-bieber-shots-of-me/|archive-date=2020-08-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 企业生涯 ==
2010年1月，约翰·沙希迪和他的弟弟山姆建立了一间移动游戏公司名为[[RockLive|RockLive]]。在RockLive建立之前，沙希迪任职为[[弗洛伊德·梅威瑟|弗洛伊德·梅威瑟]]的品牌经理。梅威瑟后来成为沙希迪移动应用的投资者。<ref name="fortune">{{cite web|title=Money Mayweather's $1 million tech punch|url=http://fortune.com/2014/06/17/floyd-mayweather-tech/|accessdate=26 August 2014|author=Roberts, Daniel|date=17 June 2014|publisher=Fortune|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121222643/https://fortune.com/2014/06/17/floyd-mayweather-tech/|archive-date=2021-01-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>该公司发行了[[Chad_Johnson|Chad Johnson]], [[迈克·泰森|迈克·泰森]], [[克里斯蒂亚诺·罗纳尔多|克里斯蒂亚诺·罗纳尔多]]和[[尤塞恩·博尔特|尤塞恩·博尔特]]的相关游戏。<ref>{{cite web|title=RockLive and Olympian Usain Bolt Release Addictive Mobile Game With the Help of Celebrity Friends|url=http://pando.com/2012/07/17/rocklive-and-olympian-usain-bolt-release-addictive-mobile-game-with-the-help-of-celebrity-friends/|accessdate=2 September 2014|author=Carney, Michael|date=17 July 2012|publisher=Pando Daily|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190420104543/https://pando.com/2012/07/17/rocklive-and-olympian-usain-bolt-release-addictive-mobile-game-with-the-help-of-celebrity-friends/|archive-date=2019-04-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>沙希迪担任公司的主席和[[首席执行官|首席执行官]]。2013年, RockLive更名为Shots.

2013年5月约翰·沙希迪和他的弟弟和[[贾斯汀·比伯|贾斯汀·比伯]]合作开发了一个自拍社交移动应用程序名为[[Shots:_拍照社交应用|Shots]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=Friends in high places (including Justin Bieber), this founder keeps it low key|url=http://upstart.bizjournals.com/entrepreneurs/hot-shots/2014/04/11/john-shahidi-teams-with-justin-bieber.html?page=all|accessdate=2 September 2014|author=Dalenberg, Alex|date=11 April 2014|publisher=Upstart Business Journal|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141108150656/http://upstart.bizjournals.com/entrepreneurs/hot-shots/2014/04/11/john-shahidi-teams-with-justin-bieber.html?page=all|archive-date=2014-11-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>该应用的目的是要为用户提供一个安全和没有网络欺凌的环境。<ref name="mashable">{{cite web|title=A-List Investors, 1 Million Downloads: Is Selfie App 'Shots' For Real?|url=http://mashable.com/2014/04/12/shots-selfie-app/|accessdate=2 September 2014|author=Wagner, Kurt|date=12 April 2014|publisher=Mashable|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200916235725/https://mashable.com/2014/04/12/shots-selfie-app/|archive-date=2020-09-16|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="techly">{{cite web|title=There's a Social Network for Selfies, and Bieber is an Investor|url=http://www.techly.com.au/2014/08/20/theres-social-network-selfies-beiber-investor/|accessdate=2 September 2014|author=Speight, Janek|date=20 August 2014|publisher=Techly|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141108020319/http://www.techly.com.au/2014/08/20/theres-social-network-selfies-beiber-investor/|archive-date=2014-11-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref>沙希迪有反对网络欺凌的想法是因为他曾经是被欺凌的受害者。<ref name="mashable" />该应用现在可以在[[安卓|安卓]]和[[iOS|iOS]]下载。<ref name="techcrunch" /><ref name="techly" />

